So the correct CSS should be `.mint-cell:active .mint-cell-mask::after` or perhaps on the cell anchor itself. The current CSS `.mint-cell-mask:active::after` would only activate if the mask element itself is clicked, but since the mask is 0×0 and invisible, it can never be clicked!

